submission_title: Friendly Reminder To Drop Winter Courses That You Don't Want Anymore :)
author: whatatimetobealiver
body: That'd be dope because I had a lil menty B and switched all my courses for the winter and my number on the waitlist hasn't changed in 2 weeks :))) so if you already know you won't be taking a certain class in the winter you could make a lot of waitlisted peeps happy by dropping sooner than later :))) have an amazing thanksgiving xo
